OL,3,CIs Vladimir Putin using body doubles?
OL,5,FAre the clips you're seeing on socials
OL,6,For in news bulletins really Vladimir
OL,7,FPutin? That's the question that has
OL,8,Fresurfaced once again after a meeting
OL,9,Fbetween the Russian president and one
OL,10,Fof his deputies.
OL,12,FIt is a popular social media
OL,13,Fconspiracy theory that President Putin
OL,14,Fuses 'lookalikes' to help conduct some
OL,15,Fforeign engagements, take press
OL,16,Fconferences or to keep him safe -
OL,17,Ffuelled by the continued silence from
OL,18,Fthe secretive state.
OL,20,FWhat can we say is really going on?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
