OL,3,CIs Vladimir Putin using body doubles?
OL,5,FDuring a televised meeting on
OL,6,FThursday, May 28, President Putin
OL,7,Fappeared to be addressed by one of
OL,8,FRussia's deputy prime ministers,
OL,9,FDmitry Patrushev, as 'Pal Laich', in
OL,10,Fan unfortunate slip of the tongue.
OL,12,FLaich, rather unfortunately, leans
OL,13,Finto the full name many online have
OL,14,Fgiven to one of the president's
OL,15,Fregularly used but unconfirmed
OL,16,Flookalikes, 'Pavel Nikolaevich'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
