OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780416668
OL,3,CIs Vladimir Putin using body doubles?
OL,5,FThis may have gone unnoticed until the
OL,6,FKremlin tweaked the official
OL,7,Ftranscript handout from the meeting,
OL,8,Fchanging 'Pavel' to 'Vladimir', which
OL,9,Fpiqued some interest.
OL,11,FThis is all just speculation, but it
OL,12,Fonly adds to the chatter around the 73-
OL,13,Fyear-old's health.
OL,15,FThese unproven claims are consistently
OL,16,Fdenied by the Russian government, but
OL,17,Fafter each international appearance,
OL,18,Fsocial media is awash with body double
OL,19,Frumours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
