CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780416668
OL,3,CIs Vladimir Putin using body doubles?
OL,5,FPeople have pointed to what they see
OL,6,Fas changes in the president's
OL,7,Fappearance in front of the cameras,
OL,8,Fleading to speculation that poor
OL,9,Fhealth might be disguised by someone
OL,10,Felse appearing instead.
OL,12,FWhen Donald Trump came face-to-face
OL,13,Fwith Putin in August last year to
OL,14,Fdiscuss the ongoing war in Ukraine, a
OL,15,Fsmall corner of the internet
OL,16,Fhighlighted perceived differences in
OL,17,Fappearance in the Russian president's
OL,18,Fface, adding fuel to the body-doubles
OL,19,Frumour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
