OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780416668
OL,3,CIs Vladimir Putin using body doubles?
OL,5,FSeparately, when Vladimir Putin met
OL,6,FChina's President Xi last year, the
OL,7,Fpair were caught on mic talking about
OL,8,Fimmortality, suggesting humans might
OL,9,Fbe able to replace their organs and
OL,10,Fthen live on.
OL,12,FPutin has also commented in the past
OL,13,Fthat plans to use doubles were
OL,14,Freportedly handed to him by his
OL,15,Fofficials more than 20 years ago -
OL,16,Fsomething he says he turned down.
OL,18,FThe claims all remain unproven - but
OL,19,Fnothing the secretive Russian state
OL,20,Fhas said so far has put any of this to
OL,21,Fbed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
